# Advertorial Builder - Development Rules

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 16 (App Router)
- React 19 + TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS v4
- shadcn/ui components
- @dnd-kit for drag-and-drop
- Supabase for backend

## Design Tokens
- Brand Teal: #0dadb7 (icons, accents)
- Brand Purple: #4644B6 (CTAs, active states)
- Brand Gray: #F6F6F6 (backgrounds)

## Key Principles
- Keep components simple and maintainable
- Use shadcn/ui for UI primitives
- Follow existing design patterns from prototype
- All state management via React hooks (no Redux/Zustand yet)
- Mobile-first responsive design

## File Structure
- app/ - Next.js pages and layouts
- components/ - React components (step-campaign-setup.tsx, step-reference-pages.tsx, step-building-blocks.tsx, step-insights.tsx, step-review.tsx)
- components/ui/ - shadcn/ui primitives
- lib/ - Utility functions (to be created)

## Current Status
- Frontend prototype complete (6-step wizard)
- Backend integration needed (n8n workflows)
- Authentication planned (Supabase Auth)